Interface ApplicableUnaryGraphToGraphOperator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Operator, UnaryCollectionToCollectionOperator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplyAggregation, ApplySubgraph, ApplyTransformation

    public interface ApplicableUnaryGraphToGraphOperator
extends UnaryCollectionToCollectionOperator
    A marker interface for instances of UnaryGraphToGraphOperator that support the application on each element in a graph collection.
